{
  "bookId": "laozi-heshanggong-wiki",
  "num": 5,
  "title": "第五章（虛用）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "天地不仁，"
    },
    {
      "text": "以萬物為芻狗。"
    },
    {
      "text": "聖人不仁，"
    },
    {
      "text": "以百姓為芻狗。"
    },
    {
      "text": "天地之間，"
    },
    {
      "text": "其猶橐籥乎。"
    },
    {
      "text": "虛而不屈，動而愈出。"
    },
    {
      "text": "多言數窮，"
    },
    {
      "text": "不如守中。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天施地化，不以仁恩，任自然也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天地生萬物，人最為貴，天地視之如芻草狗畜，不貴望其報也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人愛養萬民，不以仁恩，法天地行自然。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人視百姓如芻草狗畜，不貴望其禮意。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天地之間空虛，和氣流行，故萬物自生。人能除情慾，節滋味，清五臟，則神明居之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "橐籥中空虛，人能有聲氣。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言空虛無有屈竭時，動搖之，益出聲氣也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "多事害神，多言害身，口開舌舉，必有禍患。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不如守德於中，育養精神，愛氣希言。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
